Hi, I just submitted my major declaration form (and have the 3.3 so will make it in). I am currently on the wait list for CS 170, and CS 186, and from my understanding the waitlist clears after phase 1 and all declared people are given priority. Would it be dumb to drop off the wait list now so I can enroll in a breadth class that I'm worried may fill up, but is not as important to me to get in as 170/186? Basically what I'm asking, is am I pretty much guaranteed to get into 170 & 186 if i am declared before phase 2, and will I be able to get into them if I phase 2 them?
